// Labelers which assign new tags depending on resource properties
// Grammar:
//      first name is the new tag
//      t: - needed tags
//      >=, <= sizes
//      mÐ¼ - isMovable
//      rs - isResisting
//
-goodForClothes          t:flexible   t:solid       t:soft

